    "3. RH2M and QV2M (0.87) — [Strong Positive Correlation]:- The strong link between Relative Humidity and Specific Humidity (QV2M) confirms that Kenya’s moisture is driven by maritime air masses. When the air is humid, it is because it is physically carrying more water vapor from the ocean, not just cooling down.\n",
